name: jd2021-installer-debugging
description: 'Debug JD2021 map installer issues with an installer-first workflow. Use for map import failures, missing media, AMB/audio sync problems, preview playback issues, and regressions after code edits. Includes targeted pytest/import validation, cwd/environment checks, and known project pitfalls.'
